findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges that can be used to change fees, maximum transaction amount, exclude from fee and maxTx, enable/disable reflection fees, change reflectionInc and pairValue, change Uniswap pair, change token2 address, enable trading, burn tokens, lock and unlock, and retake privileges even after ownership was renounced.
findings.function: Multiple functions (e.g. setFeePercent, setBuyFee, setSellFee, setReflectionFees, changeBonusValues, setLpAddress, setToken2, startTrading)
